<div class="py-10 px-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
    
    <h1 class="text-3xl mb-5">Terms of Service</h1>

    <div class="w-full h-full sm:w-1/2 mt-5 flex flex-col justify-center">

        <span class="font-semibold my-3">1. Do I need to set up an account to place an order?</span>
        <p>Yes, You need to setup an account to place an order. Its quiet simple. Click on the user icon on the top right corner. Register if you haven't before. Login if you already have an account.</p>

        <span class="font-semibold my-3">2. How do I select items to purchase?</span>
        <p>As you browse through the Website, click on the Add to Cart button for the items that you wish to purchase.</p>

        <span class="font-semibold my-3">3. How do I place an order on the Website?</span>
        <p>Once your desired item is added to the shopping cart just click on the shopping cart icon on the top right corner and click on the checkout button, make sure to be logged in. Then you have to provide your personal details, click on the place order button. Your order is booked and confirmed.</p>

        <span class="font-semibold my-3">4. What are your payment options?</span>
        <p>Currently, we only have <b>Cash On Delivery (COD)</b></p>

        <span class="font-semibold my-3">5. How much does shipping cost?</span>
        <p>Nationwide delivery in PKR 250 only.</b></p>

        <span class="font-semibold my-3">6. What are your Delivery Areas?</span>
        <p>We deliver all over Pakistan through courier services.</b></p>

        <span class="font-semibold my-3">7. What happens if I receive a damaged product/item?</span>
        <p>Take a picture of your parcel and send it to this number (+92 000 00000). Our Customer Care Service will assist you shortly.</b></p>

        <span class="font-semibold my-3">8. Are Prices inclusive of applicable taxes?</span>
        <p>Yes, all prices are inclusive of applicable taxes</b></p>

    </div>

</div>

